  <h1>What is Git?</h1>
  <div class="artmeta"><span>By Coldwast</span><span>Updated Jun 14, 2026</span><span>7 min read</span><span class="tag">#git</span><span class="tag">#tools</span><span class="tag">#workflow</span></div>
